parcel.name: Angie Taylor's London Gallery
parcel.description:
Angie Taylor's London Gallery - displaying sculpture, digital art & animation. Features a permanent exhibition of artist, Angie Taylor as well as other emerging digital artists. 

Shops and studios on-site also sell wearables - clothes, art, sculpture and music.
